descriptionHTML:
Presenting "Jesus Christ Watch Face" which is a unique and intelligent Smart Watch application that features beautiful watch faces of Jesus Christ with best in class User Interface for customization.
The carefully crafted design of the app syncs up your mobile and your smart watch seamlessly and provides rich user experience making it simple and easy to use.

The unique features of this Smart Watch app are:
• Watch Face can be set to change every hour
• Analog and Digital Dial available
• High Quality and Beautiful images of Jesus Christ
comments: I love this app I think it is awesome!
